Sophie Lichaba (a mụrụ na 29 June 1973), nke a mụrụ Mphasane, nke bụbu Sophie Ndaba, bụ onye na-eme ihe nkiri na South Africa. Ọ rụrụ Queen Moroka na ncha Generations N'afọ 2016, ọ bụ onye ọka ikpe ọbịa na asọmpi ịma mma Miss South Africa 2016.
Ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ sekọndrị na Zimbabwe, mgbe nke ahụ gasịrị ọ gara n'ihu n'ọrụ ya dịka onye na-ese ihe
Nne ya zigara ya n'ụlọ ụmụ mgbei na Eastlea, Harare, Zimbabwe ka o wee nwee ike inweta agụmakwụkwọ ka mma karịa ihe dị na South Africa.
Nna Lichaba, Solly Mphasane, nwụrụ n'afọ 2016. Ọ na-arịa ọrịa shuga. Ya na di mbụ ya, Themba Ndaba, nwere ụmụ abụọ, Rudo na Lwandle
Ọ kuchiri nwa nwanne ya nwanyị, Shallon Ndaba, mgbe ọnwụ nwanne ya nwanyị gasịrị, Tiny Mphasane. Ọ lụrụ Max Lichaba n'afọ 2017. Na ngwụcha afọ 2018, Lichaba bụ onye asịrị, nke kwuru na ọ nwụọla.
